        <p>
         <em>
          This is a sponsored post written by me on behalf of Mom Central Consulting and Zappos.com. We are super excited to be part of the Zappos.com Ambassador Program for the back-to-school season. All opinion, and love for the awesome back-to-school items from Zappos.com is our own.
         </em>
        </p>
        <p>
         Summer goes by all to quickly, and before you can turn around youre sending the kids back to school. This year everything came all to fast for me and I ended updoing a lot of last-minute
         <em>
          <strong>
           back to school shopping
          </strong>
         </em>
         . I had traveled so much I let the season get away from me, and before I knew it, I was out-of-town and the kids grandmother was there for the kids first day of school. Im thankful she was there, but still a little upset I wasnt the one taking them on their first day of school. Either way, I wasnt prepared and when I got home I found myself doing the last-minute back to school shopping.
        </p>
        <h2>
         <a href="http://www.jennsblahblahblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/5-Reasons-To-Shop-Zappos.com-For-Back-To-School-Shopping.png">
          <img alt="5 Reasons To Shop Zappos.com For Back To School Shopping" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-53982 wp-image-esh" height="1050" src="http://www.jennsblahblahblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/5-Reasons-To-Shop-Zappos.com-For-Back-To-School-Shopping-700x1050.png" width="700"/>
         </a>
         5 Reasons To Shop Zappos.com For Back To School Shopping
        </h2>
        <p>
         If youre in the same place, dont panic you can still get everything you need to send you kids to school easily with
         <a href="http://zapwow.me/B5jD" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">
          Zappos.com
         </a>
         .
        </p>
        <p>
         <strong>
          Fast &amp; Free Shipping
         </strong>
          One reason I have always loved shopping at Zappos is their super-fast shipping!  You gett FREE shipping on all domestic order placed on Zappos.com, and the best part is there is no minimum order. So if you only need to grab one thing, not to worry you still get free shipping.
        </p>
        <p>
         <strong>
          Free Returns
         </strong>
          If you are not happy with your purchase, Zappos takes good care of their customers. Of course, your returns cannot be worn, and must be in the state you received them. I have used Zappos.com returns in the past, and the experience was great.
        </p>
        <p>
         <strong>
          Everything you need in one place
         </strong>
          Zappos.com has everything you need in one place. When I was ordering the kids cloths for school, I picked me up a new set up dishes too. From back to school, shopping to bed and bath items Zappos.com has everything you need.
        </p>
        <p>
         <strong>
          24/7 Customer Service
         </strong>
          You can also use their 24/7 customers service by calling their 1800 number, or chatting for live help. I have used their live help, its fast, east and everyone has always been knowledgeable and super friendly.
        </p>
        <p>
         <strong>
          Brands
         </strong>
          Zappos is awesome because they have everything from Lucky brand to Levi brand and plenty more. It makes shopping for the
         <a href=" http://www.jennsblahblahblog.com/category/family/" title="family">
          family
         </a>
         easy. I tend to be a fan of Levi brand jeans, and my oldest daughter wants Lucky brand. Either way its easy to get everything we need from one place.
        </p>
        <p>
         We received a $300 credit to purchase items from Zappos.com and I couldnt be happier with what we received, and I think my youngest Mattie is the happiest with her Skip Hop Zoo Pack Backpack, which is super cute and the perfect size for her to take the things she needs to Tuesday  Thursday school this year.
        </p>
        <p>
         <a href="http://www.jennsblahblahblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/Zappos-2.jpg">
          <img alt="Zappos (2)" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-53980" height="836" src="http://www.jennsblahblahblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/Zappos-2-700x836.jpg" width="700"/>
         </a>
         The Skip Hop Zoo Pack Backpack has a large main compartment so she can store her books, toys, or other larger items. The smaller front pocket for all those small items she is going to want to take to school. I love that there is only two pockets, which makes it easy for her to keep track of where she puts things. The cool thing about the
         <a href="%20http://zapwow.me/B5hs" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">
          Skip Hop Zoo Pack Backpack
         </a>
         is that you can get it in tons of fun different animals, and they are all cute.
        </p>
        <p>
         <a href="http://www.jennsblahblahblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/Back-to-school-shopping.jpg">
          <img alt="Back to school shopping" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-53979" height="1022" src="http://www.jennsblahblahblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/Back-to-school-shopping.jpg" width="700"/>
         </a>
         <a href="http://zapwow.me/B5jp" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">
          Lucky Brand Kids Mix n Match Lucky Logo Tee
         </a>
         is super cute, and Mattie and I both loved the fun bright color and Lucky brand logo on the front. Mattie is into the coral color, and this is her new favorite shirt. She is honestly having a hard time waiting to wear it to school. She was so excited when I told her she had to try on her new clothes for me to take a picture, and I have to admit she looked pretty darn cute. The Lucky Brand Kids Mix n Match Lucky Logo Tee has shortRaglansleeves, round neckline, features a fun colorful embroidered logo on the front, curved hem, and isslubcotton-poly jersey fabric. Naturally, I need something easy to machine wash too. The Lucky Brand shirt is just that  machine wash cold, and tumble dry low.
        </p>
        <p>
         My youngest daughter is hard to buy jeans for, because she is tall and learn. I decided to try a pair of
         <a href="http://zapwow.me/B5h0" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">
          Lucky Brand Kids Zoe Jeggings
         </a>
         , which fit her great and look amazing. They are super-stretchy jegging sports a straight fit and a slim, straight leg, which fits her perfectly.
        </p>
        <p>
         <a href="http://www.jennsblahblahblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/back-to-school-shopping-at-zappos.jpg">
          <img alt="back to school shopping at zappos" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-53981" height="784" src="http://www.jennsblahblahblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/back-to-school-shopping-at-zappos-700x784.jpg" width="700"/>
         </a>
         Converse Chuck Taylor All Star Dainty Ox  My oldest daughter started wearing Converse shoes several years ago, and that is the only brand shoe she will wear. I am in no way joking, and I dont know if that will ever change about her. However, this is the first pair of Converse that is not black, so we are making progress. She did tell me these were her favorite Converse yet, I think its the color, but she said they are super comfortable and light. I feel the shoes are true to their size, but then again I honestly dont know if Catie wears a different shoe size in other shoes because she will not wear them. The
         <a href="http://zapwow.me/B5hZ" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">
          Converse Chuck Taylor All Star Dainty Ox
         </a>
         have a five-eye-lace-up-front with metallic eyelets detail, the signature Chuck Taylor rubber toe box, textured rubber toe bumper, contrast sidewall trim, medial side dual air vent holes, and the awesome All Star heal patch.
        </p>
        <p>
         <a href="http://www.jennsblahblahblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/jeans.jpg">
          <img alt="jeans" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-53983" height="1042" src="http://www.jennsblahblahblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/jeans.jpg" width="700"/>
         </a>
         I also got my oldest daughter a pair of
         <a href="http://zapwow.me/B5jb" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">
          Levis Juniors 524 Skinny Stunner jeans
         </a>
         , which she loves. Normally shes the one who likes to wear Lucky Brand jeans, but I decided to buy here the Levis, because I thought she would like them, and GO MOM, she loves them! Not only does she loves them, but they look great on her, especially with her not black Converse shoes, lol. I am proud of my daughter for trying new things and stepping out of her comfort zone, even if she didnt have a choice with the jeans lol.
        </p>
        <p>
         Most of you know we are redoing our house too, and well we just started on the heart of our home  the kitchen. I couldnt help myself, since Zappos.com has everything from back-to-school items to beautiful items for the home I got something for mom too! I cannot recommend Zappos.com enough for all your back-to-school shopping!
        </p>
        <p>
         Swing by and check out Zappos.com for your back-to-school needs, as well as your notso back-to-school needs, lol! Were loving
         <a href="http://zapwow.me/B5jD" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">
          Zappos.com
         </a>
         !
        </p>
